(3) A person must not be:
(a) a director of a company that is in a position to exercise control of a commercial television broadcasting licence; and (b) a director of a company that is in a position to exercise control of another commercial television broadcasting licence;
if each of those licences have the same licence area.

(4) A person must not be:
(a) a director of a company that is in a position to exercise control of a commercial television broadcasting licence; and (b) in a position to exercise control of another commercial television broadcasting licence;
if each of those licences have the same licence area.

