 providing a mechanism for the issue of a licence in 2 station markets (items 19, 23, 41, 44, and 54 of Schedule 1); and  enabling a licensee allocated an additional licence to multichannel the existing and new services in SDTV digital mode on the one channel (item 86 of Schedule 1);
